{"tid":1404601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍開除2華籍士兵 理由：你爺爺做過解放軍","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T12:48:46.000Z","uid":28765,"like":95,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"66d78ed6755a65305da76612d78401b54bc61986","tid":1404601,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:18:10.000Z","msg":"美軍因為家因庭因素，開除兩名華籍士兵。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部過去幾年才啟動一特別招募計畫，希望可以真的對移民有妥善的發展規劃，提到美軍希望可以擁有中文、俄文、阿拉伯文的移民人才加入，但近日卻被發現，已經有來自中國的移民，被踢出軍隊，其原因跟家族經歷有關。<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》報道，遭美軍開除的兩名中國人，其中一人李自成（Zi Cheng Li）是因為祖父曾被中共俘虜虐待；另一名男子則是因為祖父曾經加入過解放軍，因此這兩理由美軍要求不得參軍。<br />\n<br />\n美軍不只對華籍的志願軍人進行調查，五角大廈2008年推出的MAVNI「緊缺人才徵兵計畫」，光是10年就招募約1萬人。可是，部份想加入美軍的移民，因為父母是外國人，或是家庭內曾有親屬參加過自己國家的軍隊，會被五角大廈淘汰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李自成對外媒表示，當時自己滿心期待加入美軍，卻在3個月的等待後，只得到一封郵件說道「你的條件不適合」，最後才知道竟是因為祖父曾為共產黨的俘虜，「這讓我們家人相當震驚」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190803/59892862\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190803%2F59892862&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USEzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=a9b602db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190803%2F59892862&h=a93449c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190803/59892862</a>"},{"pid":"b18368c44b9fb527b8b4147158a1caab007a3761","tid":1404601,"uid":144626,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:20:02.000Z","msg":"李自成，闖王梗係唔做美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ab985dd94b1d14d879785d331f257fad6193ba","tid":1404601,"uid":94828,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:20:14.000Z","msg":"李自成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae846827cd2782d54768f7de597d7823e9ff3b96","tid":1404601,"uid":164920,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"黎香港搞招聘會啦，大把香港義民想加入美軍。政治上絕對可靠"},{"pid":"af11fbf92f4037fef5997e2a8607f15d8cceeb8c","tid":1404601,"uid":90704,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"你知唔知上次佢失業搞到幾大鑊呀？"},{"pid":"3a2b44ad34192df9278196458f3c5ac0d7235b63","tid":1404601,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:24:20.000Z","msg":"連自己屋企都唔知嘅野 美國點查到<br />\n<br />\n仲要咁多人投考 個個查咪要好大人力物力"},{"pid":"46987c57512f64da2039db101205a708fac07236","tid":1404601,"uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a2b44ad34192df9278196458f3c5ac0d7235b63","tid":1404601,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:24:20.000Z","msg":"連自己屋企都唔知嘅野 美國點查到<br />\n<br />\n仲要咁多人投考 個個查咪要好大人力物力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:14:32.000Z","msg":"可能有其他中國人眼紅, 督灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a971517756c2038b20abb7a4ae1ffd0e5bb7e2d","tid":1404601,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"正解<br />\n已經入滲得太癲"},{"pid":"9b572b9c3bd2c49213fa2dc8a6fcd1d966d4fa35","tid":1404601,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:17:44.000Z","msg":"曾被中共俘虜虐待 睇錯係爺爺虐待人"},{"pid":"d34ac72622b3f09f5b271181eb7c9569b3672876","tid":1404601,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d498a1f8d6a57e1dedf8dc3e21d4e390f23b0b16","tid":1404601,"uid":142233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:20:53.000Z","msg":"有無吳三桂"},{"pid":"185eb33f6e1a91829a026de2